806
00:36:18,440 --> 00:36:18,960
Nuo.

807
00:36:19,320 --> 00:36:19,840
Nuo.

808
00:36:21,760 --> 00:36:22,239
Nuo.

809
00:37:02,639 --> 00:37:03,840
Hello. Welcome.

810
00:37:04,920 --> 00:37:05,920
Two cups of espresso.

811
00:37:06,119 --> 00:37:07,599
Sure. Two cups of espresso.

812
00:37:15,840 --> 00:37:16,960
Two espressos.

813
00:37:18,159 --> 00:37:18,639
Thank you.

814
00:37:44,719 --> 00:37:45,440
Is something wrong

815
