824
00:38:29,880 --> 00:38:30,840
I won't bring you trouble.

825
00:38:31,920 --> 00:38:32,719
Four espressos.

826
00:38:33,840 --> 00:38:34,760
I'll take them out.

827
00:38:41,000 --> 00:38:42,079
Make four espressos.

828
00:38:42,440 --> 00:38:43,119
Don't provoke her.

829
00:39:14,757 --> 00:39:16,687
♪The fridge keeps♪

