♪Steady hum♪

832
00:39:22,257 --> 00:39:23,520
♪That expired♪

833
00:39:23,520 --> 00:39:26,200
♪Discount flyer♪

834
00:39:27,412 --> 00:39:31,127
♪Still hangs on the door♪

835
00:39:32,287 --> 00:39:34,727
♪I'm afraid to face♪

836
00:39:34,727 --> 00:39:38,347
♪This room of polished decay♪

837
00:39:39,797 --> 00:39:41,127
♪Neon seeps♪

838
00:39:41,127 --> 00:39:44,287
