♪With the last of the hard liquor♪

840
00:39:52,967 --> 00:39:55,367
♪The darkness is so thick♪

841
00:39:55,367 --> 00:39:57,727
♪Like freshly poured asphalt♪

842
00:39:57,727 --> 00:39:59,367
