850
00:41:14,079 --> 00:41:15,639
When I was in prison,
I thought for a long time.

851
00:41:16,599 --> 00:41:18,000
(Tomb of Chen Liyang)
When I came out to see you,

852
00:41:18,199 --> 00:41:19,039
